file_content.text: All right. I surrender. Don't shoot.
I was wondering when someone was going to get around to shortening "his excellence" by a head.
I won't get in your way.
Just walk next to me a moment. There. That was painless....
You don't sound very supportive for a man who's supposed to protect Councillor Caicos with his life....
You're no good at this job.
I took this spot for the money. Go get that traitorous son of a Hutt.
Shut up! Use your brains to let me in before I splatter them on the grass.
Let me in or you die!
That's what I was trying to... never mind.
